This is a sample project which explains how to introduce interceptors to your Spring boot application. The steps are given below:-

1. Write an interceptor class which implements the HandlerInterceptor interface.
  a. Override the preHandle, postHandle and afterCompletion methods.
2. Register the interceptor class by implementing the WebMvcConfigurer interface. Override the addInterceptor method and add
your interceptor to the InterfaceRegistry.

The code snippet is inside.
